extends ../../layout

block style
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/lib/swiper/css/swiper.min.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/css/my.swiper.css')
block content
  include ../../component/navbar.pug
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-3
        include ../component/menu.pug
      .col-md-9
        h2 nested
        p 用于嵌套相同方向的swiper时，当切换到子swiper时停止父swiper的切换。
        p 请将子swiper的nested设置为true。
        p 由于需要在slideChangeEnd时判断作用快，因此快速滑动时这个选项无效。
        h4 nested参数
        p 类型：<span class="label label-info">boolean</span> 默认：<span class="label label-info">false</span> 举例：<span class="label label-info">true</span> 启用版本：<span class="label label-info">3.3.0</span>
        h4 效果演示
        .desc
          .swiper-container#e1
            .swiper-wrapper
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide 
                .swiper-container#e2
                  .swiper-wrapper
                    .swiper-slide slider2.1
                    .swiper-slide slider2.2
                    .swiper-slide slider2.3
              .swiper-slide slider3
block script
  script(src="/lib/swiper/js/swiper.jquery.min.js")
  script(src="/js/my.swiper.js")
  script.
    $(function() {
      var e1 = new Swiper('#e1');
      var e2 = new Swiper('#e2', {
        nested: true,
        resistanceRatio: 0,
      })
    })